The 4Dvar approach is effective for performing spatiotemporal interpolation of sparse data via interpolation (covariance) functions with scales based on ocean dynamics (Bennett, 2002).</dcterms:abstract><dcterms:spatial xsi:type="dcterms:Box">northlimit=67; southlimit=50; eastlimit=-158; westlimit=-180</dcterms:spatial><dcterms:temporal>Begin 2007-01-01T10:43:00; End 2010-12-31T10:44:00</dcterms:temporal></dcTerms></metadata>